The first coworker I met at work, they ask me money, but nothing else, so yeah this guy is taking advantage of me, but Hey I am from Venezuela too, i know these people, but come on! You find new people everyday. So be patient, experience is what it takes.

Before going outside, leave your room or apartment cleaned, so when you are back you feel more relax. Like the others comments, meet the correct people you would like to spare time, not anybody, you can choose and maybe find a guy who is same as you, so you can look out each others back.
